deathsHead.name: deaths head
deathsHead.word: you notice a lonely looking girl perched on the far end of the bench, uppon further inspection, it apears to be a Death's Head moth! It seems she can't help but be drawn to the site of a protagonistic moth such as yourself.

atlas.name: atlas
atlas.word: close to the lamp, surrounded by what seems to be admirers, is a grandiose Atlas moth, towering above the others in the vicinity. your imposing presence clearly intrigues her.

tigerMoth.name: tiger moth
tigerMoth.word: Upon entering the garden, you are immediately approached by an enthusiastic tiger moth, (she's enthusiastic about a giga moth like you)

gypsyMoth.name: gypsy moth
gypsyMoth.word: around back of the rest stop, a lone Gypsy moth is looking into the building through a window. She seems awfully energetic.

lunaMoth.name: luna moth
lunaMoth.word: you look up and see total squat, but when you look back down, a well dressed babe approches, drawn in by your powerful aura. She is a luna moth, and seems entranced by your pressence.

silkMoth.name: silk moth
silkMoth.word: a magnificent silk moth catches your eye, but not as much as you've caught hers. She stands elegantly gazing at your Greek God-esk form.
